{"tid":367500,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"[技能發動] 多圖！成功捕捉高登神獸！","createTime":"2017-08-20T18:25:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-25T11:16:51.000Z","uid":665,"like":349,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2cc57b31911dc3a19625f3f9f740d7fe2ba3c174","tid":367500,"uid":665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T18:25:45.000Z","msg":"岩岩沖涼個時一拎起個花灑跌左條野落地<br />\n嚇到我彈起左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後特登戴番副眼鏡睇下咩黎既<br />\n原來係...<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/21/021753_21191ecef09bd63dc8817c30568dc0bb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F21%2F021753_21191ecef09bd63dc8817c30568dc0bb.jpg&h=ae0da6df&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n即刻搵個杯捉左佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後就搵個盒安置佢<br />\n得個沙琪瑪盒 好過冇啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/21/022025_7382c8390bd91c40477d646662098970.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F21%2F022025_7382c8390bd91c40477d646662098970.jpg&h=d9677845&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁岩我間房有兩隻蚊<br />\n打q死左佢地拎黎餵大麻成（冇錯去到呢到我決定叫佢大麻成<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/21/022134_cd9e212cab7e3437c2b1ebcc40daed65.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F21%2F022134_cd9e212cab7e3437c2b1ebcc40daed65.jpg&h=309c5c21&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我知四腳蛇要食生勾勾既蟲<br />\n但一時三刻邊到搵丫 兩隻死蚊頂住先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n大麻成既安樂窩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/21/022238_c843f554ffc3da66afd8460316d1d852.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F21%2F022238_c843f554ffc3da66afd8460316d1d852.jpg&h=0a3ba027&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/21/022303_ebb70e462c725ba070ebbef70f9cab2c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F21%2F022303_ebb70e462c725ba070ebbef70f9cab2c.jpg&h=d6d2f54f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大麻成奶腳相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/21/022354_bc32a7fbec126096678d690693e5a6a9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F21%2F022354_bc32a7fbec126096678d690693e5a6a9.jpg&h=7ee2ff63&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n心諗：呢隻乜鳩黎既呢 好撚柒呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/21/022517_e95b2b4e51665781b98d0d362be246d1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F21%2F022517_e95b2b4e51665781b98d0d362be246d1.jpg&h=f43ec45c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2f2dde132ad2267541e59cee895acdd2b5a0f741","tid":367500,"uid":61463,"like":0,"dislike":19,"score":-19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T18:32:31.000Z","msg":"打破0回覆"},{"pid":"f15e7606beffa3834b1bd9ef68ace2b6cfddb991","tid":367500,"uid":115849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T18:35:15.000Z","msg":"嘩得意"},{"pid":"13472992d119e47a662b874528ec224a82f0bca0","tid":367500,"uid":69083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T18:41:19.000Z","msg":"搵個大D既箱養, 放兜水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06a24ef86bed7738a4c8e7ef83ca0885a6ac96ba","tid":367500,"uid":38793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T18:43:27.000Z","msg":"正"},{"pid":"bc8b64546ff1cc999f6cf72148694e8a154b357a","tid":367500,"uid":24597,"like":8,"dislike":5,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T18:43:46.000Z","msg":"痴線 你係咪有病 咁都捉到既"},{"pid":"2df748207d8c2249c45b15adf6b738ccc4c0535c","tid":367500,"uid":665,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T18:47:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>嘩得意</blockquote><br />\n係呀 一直都覺得好得意<br />\n今日竟然比我有機會捉到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"397112ed9b0fad353e932d181f3fc10b8a89d127","tid":367500,"uid":665,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T18:48:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>搵個大D既箱養, 放兜水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我睇下聽日收工買唔買到<br />\n平時最cheap雞養龜/金魚個啲膠兜得唔得？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8451b4544bf7f301580056fe4431fd743f2b8536","tid":367500,"uid":665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T18:50:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>痴線 你係咪有病 咁都捉到既</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我係浴室捉佢個時 佢有撥黎撥去想逃走<br />\n但太濕爬唔起<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3593261414cfe0b9ea2b48a817de546adf16eb6","tid":367500,"uid":22692,"like":50,"dislike":0,"score":50,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T18:51:56.000Z","msg":"你比佢走啦"},{"pid":"618bcdca435e6491d632e071dd80f95e2270b53b","tid":367500,"uid":22692,"like":75,"dislike":27,"score":48,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T18:52:59.000Z","msg":"你要用佢既自由換黎你既開心<br />\n<br />\n唉你話我道德撚乜撚都好啦"},{"pid":"2e6389ebab169e7c087e8fc5174c540ee61a9c38","tid":367500,"uid":103306,"like":77,"dislike":0,"score":77,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T18:53:07.000Z","msg":"人地成兜仔女等住養 你就困住人"},{"pid":"ab23b5ddea6a83a470839351d765fd8a63076ea7","tid":367500,"uid":665,"like":2,"dislike":11,"score":-9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T18:53:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你比佢走啦</blockquote><br />\n上網做左research<br />\n啲人話佢地三四日唔食野都得<br />\n但如果一個禮拜都唔肯開了口食就要放生<br />\n我就睇下佢肯唔肯食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95578e96d8c9db7530e0dcd93fcba29de7b8a167","tid":367500,"uid":665,"like":49,"dislike":4,"score":45,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T19:07:47.000Z","msg":"個盒一開 三七氣流一轉<br />\n走唔走悉隨尊便<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/21/030423_496497f07a37f488a86f3acb2af50f84.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F21%2F030423_496497f07a37f488a86f3acb2af50f84.jpg&h=f61412d1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/21/030433_421b2219e909cadaaa4676a5a3a4e71f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F21%2F030433_421b2219e909cadaaa4676a5a3a4e71f.jpg&h=a6d91ade&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢隻腳仔好可愛呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/21/030453_6914f48f01cf9c714d678d731142fff9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F21%2F030453_6914f48f01cf9c714d678d731142fff9.jpg&h=7cf0c9c8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1c989e05dd2c7c1fdf941121f5b97daad6c3e646","tid":367500,"uid":31323,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T19:11:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>人地成兜仔女等住養 你就困住人</blockquote><br />\n難分真與假 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c826dad60829eb0921760df3845408f13ed86006","tid":367500,"uid":22692,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T19:12:12.000Z","msg":"感激樓主你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9a5abde97d1673d7e95a7df1c1cc44f2f127724","tid":367500,"uid":79355,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T19:13:29.000Z","msg":"你隻鸚鵡會唔會食左佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"598be8e43acd0f5826cd34a0e8bf233cc37d154a","tid":367500,"uid":665,"like":70,"dislike":0,"score":70,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T19:14:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>感激樓主你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n摸左佢幾下都唔肯走<br />\n仲遞隻手比hand hand我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後打側個盒佢就走左lu<br />\n多謝大麻成陪左我幾個鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f68df3371aa8fbc69ab1e6580b4cea4ea7e3d0c","tid":367500,"uid":665,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T19:15:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你隻鸚鵡會唔會食左佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔會 佢又要驚又要望<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed408931004a20026f6055b3ed6292204937fb99","tid":367500,"uid":84505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T19:21:12.000Z","msg":"呢隻咩品種 好似一條屎"},{"pid":"279099b0c989f96dff307a015111d085e055b998","tid":367500,"uid":18772,"like":1,"dislike":18,"score":-17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T19:25:24.000Z","msg":"印象中你係靚女絲打仲走失隻雀<br />\n定係你係男友<br />\n應該可以買D虫或者蟋蟀/草猛比佢食?"},{"pid":"517b619bb5bd41196b02952150a56110814e720a","tid":367500,"uid":87428,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy